izes and configurations it primarily consists of surface mount and leaded ceramic capacitors rf thick and thin film components tantalum capacitors film capacitors ceramic and film power capacitors super capacitors emi filters thick and thin film packages varistors thermistors inductors and resistive products the kyocera electronic devices resale segment consists of ceramic capacitors frequency control devices saw devices sensor products rf modules actuators acoustic devices and connectors produced by kyocera and resold by avx the interconnect segment consists primarily of avx interconnect automotive telecom and memory connectors manufactured by avx the company was founded in  and is headquartered in fountain inn sc expand key people avx corp board of directors nametitle current board membership john sarvis  chairman president  chief executive officer avx corp koichi kano  director avx corp tetsuo kuba  director avx corp goro yamaguchi  director kyocera korea co ltd kyocera management consulting service shanghai co ltd shanghai kyocera electronics co ltd dongguan shilong kyocera co ltd kyocera vietnam co ltd kyocera document solutions inc kyocera china sales  trading corp kyocera corp avx corp shoichi aoki  director kyocera corp avx corp tatsumi maeda  director kyocera corp avx corp donald b christiansen  independent director avx corp david a decenzo  independent director avx corp joseph stach  independent director reno subsystems canada inc avx corp expand all executives john sarvis chairman president  chief executive officer kurt p cummings chief financial officer treasurer  executive vp john lawing chief technology officer  senior vice president keith thomas senior vice president willing king senior vice presidenttantalum products koichi kano director tetsuo kuba director goro yamaguchi director shoichi aoki director tatsumi maeda director peter venuto senior vice presidentsales michael e hufnagel chief accounting officer  vpcorporate finance kathleen m kelly seni